{
  "$schema_comment": "Demo-data scenarios. Consumed by scripts/seed_demo_data.py. Add scenarios here, not in the seeding script. Every direct_event entry is merged onto a default AuditEvent skeleton. The `tokens` field accepts [min, max] for randomization. All seeded events carry correlation_id prefix 'seed-' so they can be filtered or reset cleanly.",
